<HEAD>TO Sir WATKIN WILLIAMS WYNNE, Bart.</HEAD>
<OPENER><SALUTE>SIR,</SALUTE></OPENER>
<P>EVERY one will &s;ee the propriety of dedicating an Account of North Wales to You, who po&s;&s;e&s;s &s;o con&s;ider|able a part of that Country, and yet, Sir, this is not the motive of my Addre&s;s;&mdash;it is from a
<PB N="iv" REF="4">
