nets, and &s;ometimes with &s;pea<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> that are barbed for the purpo&s;e but having pa&s;&s;ed the bridg<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> how &s;hall I expre&s;s my feelings&mdash;the dark tremendous prec<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">+pices, the rapid river roarin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> over disjointed rocks, blac<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> caverns, and i&s;&s;uing cataracts,&mdash;all &s;erve to make this the noble &s;pecimen of the Finely Horri<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> the eye can po&s;&s;ibly behold,&mdash;the Poet has not de&s;cribed, n<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> the Painter pictured &s;o gloom<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> a retreat,&mdash;'tis the la&s;t Approa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">
